query_text: Show me all First Class shipments

query_text: What is the profit margin by product category for Home Office segment?
sql:
SELECT p.category, SUM(o.profit) / SUM(o.sales) * 100 AS profit_margin
     FROM spend_data.orders o
     JOIN spend_data.customers c ON o.customer_id = c.customer_id
     JOIN spend_data.products p ON o.product_id = p.product_id
     WHERE c.segment = 'Home Office'
     GROUP BY p.category
     ORDER BY profit_margin DESC
     LIMIT 100

query_text: Which region has highest profit?

                         GROUP BY c.region
                         ORDER BY total_profit DESC
                         LIMIT 1

query_text: What is the average sales by category?

query_text: Show me supplier performance score based on lead time and defect rate
sql:
SELECT s.supplier_name, s.location, AVG(sc.lead_time) AS avg_lead_time, AVG(sc.defect_rate) AS avg_defect_rate, 
             (1.0 / NULLIF(AVG(sc.lead_time), 0)) * (1.0 - AVG(sc.defect_rate)) AS performance_score
     FROM demand_data.suppliers s
     JOIN demand_data.supply_chain sc ON s.supplier_id = sc.supplier_id
     GROUP BY s.supplier_name, s.location
     ORDER BY performance_score DESC
     LIMIT 100

query_text: Show me year-over-year sales growth by category
sql:
SELECT p.category, o.year, SUM(o.sales) as total_sales, 
             (SUM(o.sales) - LAG(SUM(o.sales)) OVER (PARTITION BY p.category ORDER BY o.year)) / NULLIF(LAG(SUM(o.sales)) OVER (PARTITION BY p.category ORDER BY o.year), 0) * 100 as yoy_growth
     FROM spend_data.orders o
     JOIN spend_data.products p ON o.product_id = p.product_id
     GROUP BY p.category, o.year
     ORDER BY p.category, o.year

query_text: Show me products that are frequently ordered together
sql:

FROM spend_data.orders o1

GROUP BY o1.product_id, o2.product_id
ORDER BY frequency DESC
LIMIT 100
